<%- include('../partials/header') %>

<main class="main-content">
    <!-- Founder Hero Section -->
    <section class="founder-hero-section" data-aos="fade-up">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row align-items-center">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <div class="founder-content">
                        <h1 class="founder-title">Meet Our Founder</h1>
                        <h2 class="founder-name">Sangita Mehra</h2>
                        <p class="founder-tagline">From Fashion Designer to Change Maker</p>
                        <p class="founder-intro">
                            "I decided to lose myself in the service of others, aiming to give at-risk kids basic amenities like food, clothes and shelter and eventually mainstream them into school."
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <div class="founder-image" data-aos="fade-left">
                        <img src="/src/images/founder/sangita-mehra-1.jpg" alt="Sangita Mehra - Founder of Spread A Smile India" loading="lazy">
                        <div class="founder-quote-overlay">
                            <blockquote>
                                "Every child deserves a chance to dream and achieve those dreams."
                            </blockquote>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Founder's Journey Section -->
    <section class="founder-journey-section" data-aos="fade-up">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-header">
                <h2 class="section-title">A Journey of Transformation</h2>
                <p class="section-description">How personal motivation became a movement for change</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="journey-content">
                <div class="journey-item" data-aos="fade-right">
                    <div class="journey-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-palette"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="journey-details">
                        <h3>The Fashion Designer</h3>
                        <p>Sangita Mehra was a successful fashion designer and entrepreneur, running her own business and part of the renowned Mehrasons Jewellers family. She had built a thriving career in the fashion industry, but something was missing.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="journey-item" data-aos="fade-left">
                    <div class="journey-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-heart-broken"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="journey-details">
                        <h3>The Awakening</h3>
                        <p>Walking through the streets of Delhi, Sangita was deeply moved by the plight of street children begging at traffic lights, living in dire conditions without access to basic necessities. This maternal compassion sparked a transformation in her life's purpose.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="journey-item" data-aos="fade-right">
                    <div class="journey-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-hand-holding-heart"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="journey-details">
                        <h3>The Decision</h3>
                        <p>In 2005, Sangita made a life-changing decision - she gave up her fashion business to devote herself entirely to social work. "I decided to lose myself in the service of others," she recalls, determined to "spread a better life" for street children.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="journey-item" data-aos="fade-left">
                    <div class="journey-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-seedling"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="journey-details">
                        <h3>The Beginning</h3>
                        <p>Starting with her older son Aashray, Sangita began with just 10 local street children in their neighborhood. What started as providing basic food, clothing, and shelter gradually evolved into informal classes and eventually school enrollment support.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Leadership Philosophy Section -->
    <section class="philosophy-section" data-aos="fade-up">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-8 mx-auto">
                    <div class="philosophy-content">
                        <h2>Leadership Philosophy</h2>
                        <div class="philosophy-grid">
                            <div class="philosophy-item">
                                <div class="philosophy-icon">
                                    <i class="fas fa-eye"></i>
                                </div>
                                <h4>Vision</h4>
                                <p>To create a future where every child born in poverty can break the cycle of destitution through education and empowerment.</p>
                            </div>
                            
                            <div class="philosophy-item">
                                <div class="philosophy-icon">
                                    <i class="fas fa-heart"></i>
                                </div>
                                <h4>Compassion</h4>
                                <p>Leading with maternal love and treating every child as her own, ensuring dignity and respect in all interactions.</p>
                            </div>
                            
                            <div class="philosophy-item">
                                <div class="philosophy-icon">
                                    <i class="fas fa-users"></i>
                                </div>
                                <h4>Community</h4>
                                <p>Building bridges between different sections of society, creating partnerships that strengthen the support system for children.</p>
                            </div>
                            
                            <div class="philosophy-item">
                                <div class="philosophy-icon">
                                    <i class="fas fa-graduation-cap"></i>
                                </div>
                                <h4>Education First</h4>
                                <p>Believing that education is the most powerful tool for transformation and sustainable change in children's lives.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Recognition and Media Section -->
    <section class="recognition-section" data-aos="fade-up">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-header">
                <h2 class="section-title">Recognition & Media</h2>
                <p class="section-description">Sangita's work has been recognized nationally and internationally</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="recognition-grid">
                <div class="recognition-item" data-aos="zoom-in">
                    <div class="recognition-icon">
                        <i class="fab fa-youtube"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h4>TEDx Talk</h4>
                    <p>"Making Lemonade From Love" - TEDxCoventGardenWomen, London</p>
                    <a href="#" class="recognition-link">Watch Talk</a>
                </div>
                
                <div class="recognition-item" data-aos="zoom-in">
                    <div class="recognition-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-newspaper"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h4>Asian Age Feature</h4>
                    <p>"Smiles of Hope" - Detailed profile in Asian Age, March 2016</p>
                    <a href="#" class="recognition-link">Read Article</a>
                </div>
                
                <div class="recognition-item" data-aos="zoom-in">
                    <div class="recognition-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-magazine"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h4>Cosmopolitan India</h4>
                    <p>Featured interview about her journey from fashion to philanthropy</p>
                    <a href="#" class="recognition-link">View Feature</a>
                </div>
                
                <div class="recognition-item" data-aos="zoom-in">
                    <div class="recognition-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-trophy"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h4>NAI Achievement Awards</h4>
                    <p>Recognition for outstanding contribution to child welfare, 2019</p>
                    <a href="#" class="recognition-link">Learn More</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Personal Message Section -->
    <section class="personal-message-section" data-aos="fade-up">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="message-content">
                <div class="message-header">
                    <h2>A Personal Message from Sangita</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="message-body">
                    <blockquote class="founder-message">
                        <p>"When I see a child who was once begging at traffic lights now sitting in a classroom, reading and writing, my heart fills with immense joy. This transformation is not just theirs - it's ours, as a society."</p>
                        
                        <p>"Every child we help is someone's hope realized. They are not just statistics or beneficiaries; they are future teachers, doctors, artists, and leaders. My journey from fashion to social work taught me that true success is measured not by what we accumulate, but by what we give back."</p>
                        
                        <p>"I invite you to join this beautiful journey of transformation. Whether you volunteer for an hour, donate a rupee, or simply spread awareness, you become part of a child's success story. Together, we can ensure that every child gets the chance to spread their own smile."</p>
                        
                        <cite>
                            <img src="/src/images/founder/sangita-mehra-2.jpg" alt="Sangita Mehra" class="signature-img">
                            <span class="signature-name">Sangita Mehra</span>
                            <span class="signature-title">Founder & Director</span>
                        </cite>
                    </blockquote>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Connect Section -->
    <section class="connect-section" data-aos="fade-up">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="connect-content">
                <h2>Connect with Sangita</h2>
                <p>Follow our founder's journey and insights on social media</p>
                <div class="social-links">
                    <a href="https://instagram.com/sangitamehra1" target="_blank" class="social-link">
                        <i class="fab fa-instagram"></i>
                        <span>@sangitamehra1</span>
                    </a>
                    <a href="#" class="social-link">
                        <i class="fab fa-facebook"></i>
                        <span>Spread A Smile India</span>
                    </a>
                    <a href="#" class="social-link">
                        <i class="fab fa-linkedin"></i>
                        <span>Sangita Mehra</span>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Call to Action -->
    <section class="cta-section" data-aos="fade-up">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="cta-content">
                <h2>Inspired by Sangita's Journey?</h2>
                <p>Join us in creating more transformation stories</p>
                <div class="cta-buttons">
                    <a href="/get-involved/volunteer" class="btn btn-primary">
                        <i class="fas fa-hands-helping"></i>
                        Start Volunteering
                    </a>
                    <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-secondary">
                        <i class="fas fa-envelope"></i>
                        Get in Touch
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</main>

